    "  3. Self-reference features\n",
    "  4. Channel/Topic features\n",
    "  5. Sentiment features\n",
    "  6. Temporal features (weekdays, weekend)\n",
    "\n",
    "Understanding these features will help us:\n",
    "- Identify which features might be most predictive\n",
    "- Detect potential multicollinearity\n",
    "- Guide feature engineering decisions"
