    "\n",
    "## Feature Engineering Opportunities\n",
    "\n",
    "Based on our EDA, here are potential new features:\n",
    "\n",
    "### 1. Content-based Features\n",
    "- `media_count`: num_imgs + num_videos (total media)\n",
    "- `content_length_per_href`: n_tokens_content / num_hrefs\n",
    "- `has_media`: boolean if num_imgs > 0 or num_videos > 0\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2. Engagement Features\n",
    "- `self_reference_ratio`: self_reference / total_hrefs\n",
    "- `keyword_score`: kw_avg_avg * (kw_min_avg + kw_max_avg) / 2\n",
    "\n",
    "### 3. Topic Combination Features\n",
    "- `topic_diversity`: entropy of LDA topics\n",
    "- `dominant_topic`: max LDA topic\n",
    "\n",
    "### 4. Sentiment Features\n",
    "- `sentiment_balance`: positive_words / negative_words\n",
    "- `sentiment_volatility`: max_positive_polarity - min_negative_polarity\n",
    "\n",
    "### 5. Temporal Features\n",
    "- `weekend_multipler`: is_weekend * kw_avg_avg\n",
    "- `day_of_week_sentiment`: interaction between weekday and sentiment\n",
    "\n",
    "### 6. Polynomial Features\n",
    "- Square of key features (kw_avg_avg², num_hrefs²)\n",
    "- Interaction between related features"
